{"changes": [{"date_iso": "2026-06-06", "date_label": "Sat.06.06.26", "description": {"new": "Barulho World returns to Annex, bringing a curated night to Dortmund that moves between club culture and global sonic landscapes.\n\nAs a collective, Barulho World stands for a perspective on\nelectronic music that centers Afro-diasporic influences\nand connects local scenes with international currents.\n\nThe musical focus lies on\nAfro-electronic sounds\nin their full range: from Afrohouse and\nAfrotech\nto\nGqom\n,\nBaile Funk\nand\nKuduro\n, extending into genre-crossing hybrid forms. Rather than fixed categories, the emphasis is on music as a connecting force.\n\nA key part of this approach is the integration of live and hybrid elements. Through hardware, performative setups, or voice, the music remains immediate and closely tied to the moment. The dancefloor becomes not only a space for listening, but for experiencing performance itself.\n\nWith Frau Beji, Piccell and D[Nowhere]J, different perspectives come together, each embodying this approach and shaping the space both sonically and emotionally.\n\nAdmission 25 €", "old": "Admission 25 €"}, "fields": {}, "floor_changes": [], "floor_subtitle_changes": [], "floors_added": [], "floors_removed": [], "id": "2026-06-06", "kind": "modified", "slot_changes": [], "title": null, "url": "https://www.openground.club/en/schedule/2026-06-06"}], "run_at": "2026-05-14T01:17:19+00:00"}
